snippet.title: What Is Momentum Mod? - Standalone Surf, Bhop, Rocket Jump and More!
snippet.description:
Momentum Mod is a free, standalone game built on the Source Engine that aims to faithfully recreate, centralize, and improve upon the movement game modes found in Counter-Strike, Team Fortress, Half-Life 2, and Titanfall.

Learn more at our website:
https://momentum-mod.org

Wishlist us on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/669270/Momentum_Mod

Consider joining our Discord server to stay up to date with the game's development:
https://discord.gg/n4v52uv

Video edited by TraZox
Narration by Beetle179
Song: Subspace Triangle by Vectorgeist
https://soundcloud.com/vectorgeist/subspacetriangle
